EN: Encouragement is one of the important means to stimulate people's potential.

ZH: 他的成功给了其他人很大的鼓励。
EN: His success has given great encouragement to others.

ZH: 遇到困难时，我们要相互鼓励，互相支持。
EN: When facing difficulties, we should encourage and support each other.

ZH: 教师要注重学生的鼓励和奖励。
EN: Teachers should pay attention to student encouragement and rewards.

ZH: 他是一个勇于接受挑战的人，给大家带来了很多鼓励。
EN: He is a person who is willing to accept challenges and brings a lot of encouragement to everyone.

ZH: 请大家鼓励一下这位运动员，他正在为国家争光。
EN: Please encourage this athlete. He is striving for national glory.
